Q. When did you go to his house again - A. Some few days after - his wife was in custody at the time;
Eliza Grew
, who is present, had the care of the house. In the chimney-piece of the upper room, between two bricks, I found two guineas and two half guineas in a small piece of paper - Mr. M'Daniel was present. I have kept them ever since.
